# except-self

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `set_operation_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (except ?all ?x ?x)
rhs: (filter (const-bool false) ?x)
